      },
      "comments": [],
      "reviews": [
        {
          "id": "PRR_kwDOIiAkrc5Ide4Y",
          "commit": {
            "abbreviatedOid": "6f590e4"
          },
          "author": "boucadair",
          "authorAssociation": "OWNER",
          "state": "APPROVED",
          "body": "",
          "createdAt": "2022-12-13T15:14:34Z",
          "updatedAt": "2022-12-13T15:21:55Z",
          "comments": [
            {
              "originalPosition": 4,
              "body": "Good point. The address should be a read-only then. ",
              "createdAt": "2022-12-13T15:14:34Z",
              "updatedAt": "2022-12-13T15:21:55Z"
            },
            {
              "originalPosition": 9,
              "body": "FWIW, the current version we have include the following at profile level\r\n\r\n```\r\n`     |  |     +--rw bgp\r\n     |  |     |  +--rw peer-groups\r\n     |  |     |     +--rw peer-group* [name]\r\n     |  |     |        +--rw name              string\r\n     |  |     |        +--rw peer-as           inet:as-number\r\n     |  |     |        +--rw address-family?   identityref`\r\n```",
              "createdAt": "2022-12-13T15:17:22Z",
              "updatedAt": "2022-12-13T15:21:55Z"
            },
            {
              "originalPosition": 13,
              "body": "How to reference a peer-group instance?",
              "createdAt": "2022-12-13T15:19:43Z",
              "updatedAt": "2022-12-13T15:21:55Z"
            },
            {
              "originalPosition": 17,
              "body": "I'm afraid the neighbor-profile needs to be further defined",
              "createdAt": "2022-12-13T15:20:12Z",
              "updatedAt": "2022-12-13T15:21:55Z"
            },
            {
              "originalPosition": 51,
              "body": "To ease identifying required changes, the structure we currently have in the yang file is provided below: \r\n\r\n```\r\n        |     +--rw bgp\r\n        |     |  +--rw peer-groups\r\n        |     |  |  +--rw peer-group* [name]\r\n        |     |  |     +--rw name              string\r\n        |     |  |     +--rw peer-as           inet:as-number\r\n        |     |  |     +--rw address-family?   identityref\r\n        |     |  +--rw neighbor* [remote-address]\r\n        |     |     +--rw remote-address    inet:ip-address\r\n        |     |     +--rw peer-group?       -> ../../peer-groups/peer-group/name\r\n        |     |     +--rw peer-as           inet:as-number\r\n        |     |     +--rw address-family?   identityref\r\n        |     |     +--rw status\r\n        |     |        +--rw admin-status\r\n        |     |        |  +--rw status?        identityref\r\n        |     |        |  +--rw last-change?   yang:date-and-time\r\n        |     |        +--ro oper-status\r\n        |     |           +--ro status?        identityref\r\n        |     |           +--ro last-change?   yang:date-and-time\r\n```",
              "createdAt": "2022-12-13T15:21:51Z",
              "updatedAt": "2022-12-13T15:21:55Z"
            }
          ]
        },
